<span id="fn_478"></span>[193:1](sbe2632.htm#fr_480.md) Ned idam anv
ahorâtrâ*n*i *s*o*k*ân iti, Kâ*n*va recension.

<span id="fn_479"></span>[193:2](sbe2632.htm#fr_481.md) See [III, 8, 1,
5](sbe2631.htm#3:8:1:5.md).

